lead_paragraph: CSKA Moscow's long-serving head coach Leonid Slutskiy will step down after Wednesday's Champions League match against Tottenham Hotspur at Wembley, the Russian club said in a statement.

headline.print_headline: CSKA Moscow Coach Slutskiy to Quit After Spurs Match
